{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"090e0ee3f7","title":"致邓子恢电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"48415dc078","index":0,"year":1951,"month":9,"day":24,"articleId":"090e0ee3f7"},{"id":"b3f503d459","index":1,"year":1951,"month":9,"day":25,"articleId":"090e0ee3f7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"8b5ae69c09","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"090e0ee3f7","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"邓子恢，当时任中共中央中南局第三书记。"},{"id":"dd3a39df35","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"090e0ee3f7","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"小平，即邓小平，当时任中共中央西南局第一书记。贺龙，当时任中共中央西南局第三书记。"},{"id":"3ebdfeed0c","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"090e0ee3f7","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"邓子恢1951年9月25日给毛泽东的电报中说：“我昨夜始回汉，因要了解一些工作情况，又因家母前日病故，要主持丧事，故拟于过国庆节后去京。可否，请示。”"}],"contents":[{"id":"e5859a8714","type":"title","text":"致邓子恢电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"090e0ee3f7"},{"id":"8b5ae69c09","type":"paragraph","text":"子恢同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"090e0ee3f7"},{"id":"dd3a39df35","type":"paragraph","text":"如果可能的话，希望你借同小平贺龙同志一道早日来京。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"090e0ee3f7"},{"id":"3ebdfeed0c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"090e0ee3f7"},{"id":"99b7c5fb4f","type":"paragraph","text":"九月廿四日子恢同志：","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"090e0ee3f7"},{"id":"1be3baa773","type":"paragraph","text":"九月二十五日电以悉。（一）尚你的病故的老母致衰停之意：（二）同意你于过国庆节后来京，如能于十月三日到京则甚好。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoq